comments: Awesome professor. Really helps you out with extra credit. I love her. She\'s the best psychology professor. Easy A as long as you attend classes, participate, and study!
Amazing psychology teacher! Extremely smart and generous! Very wise with students!!! Take her and you\'ll want to minor in psychology just like I did:)))

great teacher! makes class so interesting and is always showing fun videos to go along with her lectures. her extra credit is important for exams, yet she tells you exactly what you need to study before the exam.

the best psych teacher in the school! she makes class interesting, layed back and fun. you learn soo much & have a laugh while at it! she is fun & a sweetheart... 3 basic exams (including final) some extra credit, & one final paper. take her, you wont regret it!
It was a pleasure taking the class. She was alot of fun!
